OL,5, The Met Police has referred itself to  
OL,6, the police watchdog over the treatment 
OL,7, of a woman arrested in front of her son
OL,8, in Croydon, south London, after wrongly
OL,9, being accused of bus fare evasion.     
OL,11,FFootage of the mother shouting as two  
OL,12,Fofficers handcuffed and held her       
OL,13,Fprovoked criticism on social media.    
OL,15,FThe Met said she was later released    
OL,16,Fwhen it was confirmed she had paid for 
OL,17,Fher ticket.                            
OL,19,FThe force added the video was a        
OL,20,F"snapshot of a wider incident".        
